Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.33,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fs180\frx6\fry4\fr4\move(194,80,-140,80)\c&HD0D0D0&}...the messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to be the messiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a mad scientist...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I desire chaos and destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now restart Operation Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Braun's still downstairs, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, you were helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The D-mail has already changed the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world line changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, you've lost some
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of your memories from before the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this about that Lotto-6 thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you the only one who remembers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titor told me that I have a power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prove it, we need to move world lines again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to retain memories, \Neven across world line changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic eye: Reading Steiner.
Comment: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:46.09,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.86,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}suujuuoku mono kodou no kazu sae
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.86,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the world's billions of heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:11.79,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}anata ni wa matataki teido no saji na toukyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:11.79,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are nothing to you but a fleeting and insignificant question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:16.83,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kako ni torawarete mirai wo nageku mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:16.83,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We may be trapped in the past or lament the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:22.76,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}chiri hitotsu gosan wo yurusanu hitsuzen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:22.76,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But predetermination does not allow the slightest mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:29.01,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}mugen ni hirogaru yume mo egaku mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:29.01,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The infinite dreams and imagined futures before us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:34.81,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}bokutachi ni yurusareta kyoei no genri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:34.81,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are naught but vain theories we may hold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:40.86,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}yuugen sore wa futatsu no hari ga shimesu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:40.86,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}Finitude is what the two clock hands show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:45.61,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}zankoku na yakujou to sentaku e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:45.61,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}As they point toward a cruel destiny and choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.53,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:54.75,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}dakara ima ichibyou goto ni sekaisen wo koete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:54.75,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}And now I cross the boundary between worlds each second
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:59.79,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kimi no sono egao mamoritai no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:59.79,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because I want to protect that smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:06.72,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}soshite mata kanashimi no nai jikan no ruupu e to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:06.72,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And a loop in time without sadness will once again
